systematic study of the interplay between novel topological\nquantum states with emergent effects and competing order induced by strongly\ncorrelated electrons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 16:27:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-31"}
