iments on Drosophila gene expression data sets\ndemonstrate the efficiency and the effectiveness of the proposed algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 18:04:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Dec 2014 07:03:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-10"}
