hedrops and their polar duals are established. For example,\nthe free polar dual of a free spectrahedrop is again a free spectrahedrop. We\nalso give a Positivstellensatz for free polynomials that are positive on a free\nspectrahedrop.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 20:11:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Feb 2016 01:27:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-27"}
