bb Z$ and $\\mathbb T$. For rational\nrotations of $\\mathbb T$, this implies that the structure space is homeomorphic\nto $\\mathbb T^2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 09:31:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 07:37:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
