ial-based solutions, we illustrate by means of simulation some\ncontent-oblivious/oriented proposals in scenarios based on synthetic mobility\npatterns and real human traces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 10:19:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-01"}
