actly\nthe enstrophy one of two-dimensional Euler by Kraichan), simultaneous forward\ntransfers (with $s(k)=constant$), or even no simply-directed transfer (with,\nsay, non-monotonic $s(k) \\propto \\sin^2k$), besides the inverse-energy and\nforward-helicity dual transfers (with, say, $s(k)=k$ as in the homochiral\ncase).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 13:43:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-01"}
